test_zero_range:
assert [0, 0, 0] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 0, 0]
test_even_range:
assert [174, 176, 178] == [176, 178]
  At index 0 diff: 174 != 176
  Left contains one more item: 178
  Full diff:
  - [176, 178]
  + [174, 176, 178]
  ?  +++++
test_large_range:
assert [87, 88, 89] == [88, 89]
  At index 0 diff: 87 != 88
  Left contains one more item: 89
  Full diff:
  - [88, 89]
  + [87, 88, 89]
  ?  ++++
